                   , byteable
                   , HUnit
                   , QuickCheck >= 2
                   , test-framework >= 0.3.3
                   , test-framework-quickcheck2 >= 0.2.9
                   , test-framework-hunit
                   , cryptohash

Benchmark bench-hashes
  Main-Is:           Bench.hs
  hs-source-dirs:    Bench
